Subject: drm/amdgpu: add invalidate semaphore limit for SRIOV in gmc10
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: f271fe1856138d402e0438f994ccae95f9044b2c
